data.text:
This is a DTF (direct to film) transfer.

COLOR: Full Color

SIZE: 10.6x9.8"

TEMPERATURE: 285-310 Degrees Fahrenheit, Medium/Heavy Pressure

PRE-PRESS: Pre-press fabric (not transfer) for 5-7 seconds to remove wrinkles & moisture.

INSTRUCTIONS: Cover transfer with parchment paper or a Teflon sheet to prevent transfer from sticking to heat press. Press for 12 seconds. Wait at least 10 seconds, then peel transfer film (warm or cold peel). Recover and press for another 12 seconds.
